        "description": "Phases of the Moon is a three-dimensional poem that you fly through in order to read. It is not an ordinary text, but a place that you visit and quickly get lost in. \n\nThe narrative revolves around a toxic love story told through 60 chapters or 'phases', which intertwine in a cloud of text strings. As the reader and protagonist move closer to the center and ending of the text, its poetic statements crisscross and fuse into a chaotic conclusion.\n\nThe full journey is 20 minutes.\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\n• Hold the trigger buttons to fly\n• Control the speed by bending and stretching your arms\n• You can fly with just a single controller - or both for maximum speed\n• In the menu you can access the chapter index, switch the color and more\n",
